544
01:03:32,541 --> 01:03:33,969
<i>Kau cantik sekali.</i>

545
01:03:34,143 --> 01:03:36,910
<i>Aku memberitahunya
kami akan bercerai.</i>

546
01:03:36,971 --> 01:03:38,996
<i>Kau pikir bajingan itu
akan bercerai?</i>

547
01:03:38,996 --> 01:03:41,034
<i>Tidak akan./ Maaf.</i>

548
01:03:41,034 --> 01:03:43,104
<i>Aku memohon padanya./
Kau menemuinya?</i>

549
01:03:43,104 --> 01:03:46,901
<i>Kenapa Ibu di sini?
Aku bisa jaga Ah-ram.</i>

550
01:03:46,901 --> 01:03:48,267
<i>Cepat pergi dari sini.</i>

551
01:03:48,486 --> 01:03:50,063
<i>Tolong jangan pergi.</i>

552
01:03:50,354 --> 01:03:51,789
<i>Bagimu, aku...</i>

553
01:03:52,104 --> 01:03:54,031
<i>Apa itu Ji-eun?</i>

554
01:03:54,166 --> 01:03:56,938
<i>surga atau neraka?</i>

555
01:03:57,393 --> 01:03:58,781
<i>Jika cinta kita...</i>

556
01:03:58,885 --> 01:04:01,104
<i>Maaf./ Bukan benar-benar cinta...</i>

557
01:04:01,104 --> 01:04:03,000
<i>Jangan pernah
menemui Ji-eun lagi.</i>

558
01:04:03,010 --> 01:04:07,352
<i>Cinta kita juga akan berakhir
di ujung jalan ini.</i>

559
01:04:07,549 --> 01:04:12,922
<i>Maka tetaplah seperti ini
sebentar saja...</i>